      "title": "COVID-19: 5 deaths, 181 cases reported on Saturday (13)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Government Information Department says that five COVID-19 deaths have been reported for Friday (13).",
        "The deceased are two females and three males over the age of 60.",
        "Moreover, 181 COVID-19 patients have also been reported on Saturday (13), the Government Information Department added, which brings the total number of patients reported to 667,735.",
        "Will support from Opposition until Tamil people are satisfied: C.V. Wigneswaran"
